title: website: Go Download link is down
body:
I'm trying to install Go from the link below:
https://golang.org/dl/

It redirects me here: 
https://storage.googleapis.com/golang/go1.5.1.darwin-amd64.pkg

This webpage is not available

ERR_QUIC_PROTOCOL_ERROR

The webpage at https://storage.googleapis.com/golang/go1.5.1.darwin-amd64.pkg might be temporarily down or it may have moved permanently to a new web address.
